The paper focuses on studying the learning process of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) in image classification tasks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. The paper also discusses the generalization ability of CNNs, which is a key topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) research. Additionally, the paper analyzes the visual appearances of easy and hard examples, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL) research.
